UNIX Signals
------------
- List of available signals: man 7 signal
- API
     - signal(...) - sets the handles function to be called for a certain signal
     	 	   - it does not signal anything
     - kill(...) - send the given signal to the given process
     - alarm(...) - raises a signal after a given time

EXEC
----
execl - absolute path
execlp - searches itself
execv - execl, multiple params
execvp - execlp, multiple params

P - searches the path
L - list
V - array
E - environment  variables

PIPE
----
- close the pipe ends that you do not need, as soon as possible
